response.overview: Fish that lay eggs on dry land.  Birds that navigate for thousands of miles without a map or compass.  Bats that swoop through total darkness without the slightest bump in the night.  In Dust or Destiny, you'll marvel at some of the world's most astonishing natural wonders.  And learn how each of them gives fervent testimony to the fact that this planet was not formed from ordinary dust.  But from the loving hands of a living God.
response.title: Dust or Destiny
